{"tid":2402600,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"思捷前主席邢李㷧女兒全沽思捷　套現近2億離場","createTime":"2021-02-10T13:43:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T00:38:49.000Z","uid":173272,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"01581137c4c31d72f4a68d0ee77f726c7cbe1f5d","tid":2402600,"uid":173272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:43:24.000Z","msg":"思捷環球 （00330） 早前宣布供股後，前主席邢李㷧的3名女兒邢嘉倩、邢愛林及邢言愛在場內以每股平均價0.9元，全數沽出思捷環球的股份，套現1.9億元，而三人亦不再持有思捷的股權。<br />\n<br />\n思捷環球今日收報0.99元，升5.3%，成交2.4億元。<br />\n<br />\n據聯交所股權披露顯示，邢嘉倩、邢愛林及邢言愛各佔三分一股權的Total Market Ltd於2月10月將約2.1億股或11.22%的思捷股權，以每股平均價0.9元沽售。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2876572/【ESPRIT】思捷前主席邢李㷧女兒全沽思捷%E3%80%80套現近2億離場?mtc=80010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2876572%2F%E3%80%90ESPRIT%E3%80%91%E6%80%9D%E6%8D%B7%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E9%82%A2%E6%9D%8E%E3%B7%A7%E5%A5%B3%E5%85%92%E5%85%A8%E6%B2%BD%E6%80%9D%E6%8D%B7%25E3%2580%2580%E5%A5%97%E7%8F%BE%E8%BF%912%E5%84%84%E9%9B%A2%E5%A0%B4%3Fmtc%3D80010&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=4387aeeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2876572/【ESPRIT】思捷前主席邢李㷧女兒全沽思捷%E3%80%80套現近2億離場?mtc=80010</a>"},{"pid":"8b40d07b2b24153282614f053a9a6bad6fe5e3a9","tid":2402600,"uid":23445,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:55:12.000Z","msg":"老豆d新年利是姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d0b93141d18f97e6a180ce4dc3275977b0ddfb","tid":2402600,"uid":23190,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:56:54.000Z","msg":"當年股王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f72a7e738a638720c1f3289106cc82d10ba2c86","tid":2402600,"uid":125113,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T13:57:18.000Z","msg":"仍然愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45c01b62fb4bd6981b0a7f6a37